title: Just a Trend 2/27: TrumpVirus and PenceDemic, Supreme, Dunkin' Bacon Snacks, Mayor Pete
itunes:title: Just a Trend 2/27: TrumpVirus and PenceDemic, Supreme, Dunkin' Bacon Snacks, Mayor Pete
description:
On this edition of But You Say He’s Just a Trend Jack and Miles discuss the blame thrown at Trump and Pence for public perception of Corona Virus, Supreme just released their Spring line (Oreos included), Dunkin' Donuts is releasing a new “snack”, and Pete has some interesting condiment combos.
